{
  "id": "5ae6b192b6450300145800ee",
  "title": "規模の経済",
  "created": 1525068181,
  "updated": 1525069055,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "5ae6b192b6450300145800ee",
      "text": "規模の経済",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068181,
      "updated": 1525068181
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b1a0aff09e00001252dd",
      "text": "一度にたくさん作った方が一つ当たりの生産コストが安い",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068192,
      "updated": 1525068215
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b232aff09e00001252e5",
      "text": "\t[不可分性] [分割不可能性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068339,
      "updated": 1525068820
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b414aff09e00001252f9",
      "text": " \t半分の量を作るからと言って半分のコストで済むわけではない。例:高炉",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068821,
      "updated": 1525068854
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b251aff09e00001252e7",
      "text": " [分業の利益]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068370,
      "updated": 1525068412
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b445aff09e00001252fa",
      "text": " \t大勢の労働者を雇い、分野に特化させることによって分業の利益が発生する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068869,
      "updated": 1525068886
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b237aff09e00001252e6",
      "text": "\t[経験曲線]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068343,
      "updated": 1525068415
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b254aff09e00001252e8",
      "text": " \t[労働集約的]でかつ同じ作業が繰り返される産業は、労働者の習熟によって生産性が向上する",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068372,
      "updated": 1525068960
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4a4aff09e0000125301",
      "text": "  \t[nishio.icon]だけどそういう仕事が今後コンピュータに置き換わっていくのでは",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068964,
      "updated": 1525068989
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4c1aff09e0000125304",
      "text": "  [経験曲線(けいけんきょくせん)とは - コトバンク https://kotobank.jp/word/%E7%B5%8C%E9%A8%93%E6%9B%B2%E7%B7%9A-178968]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068993,
      "updated": 1525068993
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4bfaff09e0000125303",
      "text": "\t別の切り口",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068992,
      "updated": 1525069001
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4d3aff09e000012530a",
      "text": " \t[工場設備規模の経済性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069012,
      "updated": 1525069012
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4faaff09e0000125314",
      "text": "  \t不可分性の話",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069051,
      "updated": 1525069055
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e000012530c",
      "text": "  [企業規模の経済性]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e000012530d",
      "text": "  \t[範囲の経済]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e000012530e",
      "text": "   (1)関連製品をまとめて生産することによる効率化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e000012530f",
      "text": "   (2)原材料をまとめて購入することによる効率化([買い手の交渉力])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e0000125310",
      "text": "   (3)広告の効率化、企業ブランド効果",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e0000125311",
      "text": "   (4)研究開発をまとめて行うことによる効率化、知識共有",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e0000125312",
      "text": "   (5)輸送・販売をまとめることによる効率化",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4e0aff09e0000125313",
      "text": "   (6)資金調達の規模が大きくなることによる、金額あたりの取引コストの減少",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069025,
      "updated": 1525069027
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4d1aff09e0000125307",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069010,
      "updated": 1525069010
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b4c9aff09e0000125306",
      "text": "\t規模の経済が大きいと、[参入障壁]となり[市場の失敗]の原因になる",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525069001,
      "updated": 1525069010
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b2f7aff09e00001252ef",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068535,
      "updated": 1525068535
    },
    {
      "id": "5ae6b195aff09e00001252db",
      "text": "[規模の経済(きぼのけいざい)とは - コトバンク https://kotobank.jp/word/%E8%A6%8F%E6%A8%A1%E3%81%AE%E7%B5%8C%E6%B8%88-2671]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1525068181,
      "updated": 1525068181
    }
  ]
}